Package com.soprabanking.ips.models

Class Proposal

java.lang.Object
com.soprabanking.ips.models.Proposal
@Entity
public class Proposal
extends java.lang.Object
Class representing a Process Improvement Proposal made by a given User.Specifies all the fields and relationships of Proposal entity in the database.

A User can create any number of proposals.At the time of creation of a new Proposal, user has to forward it.Only the user who is creating a proposal, can forward it to one or more Team instances. A proposal can also be shared by any user to any number of Team instances(to which it was not forwarded at the time of creation). A User can add Comment and Upvotes on a proposal.Also, the User ,who has created a proposal ,can delete or update it as well.

Author:
araghav
See Also:
User, Team, Comment, Upvotes
